[
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000000",
    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "17912648305571294",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "That light on the front nine is the whole reason to go early. Save me a spot Saturday.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-15T12:05:40+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "judith"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000001",
    "like_count": "9",
    "media_id": "17923085164729038",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "She did not want to leave that pond. Thanks for tiring her out before the drive home, Dad.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-15T18:45:24+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "brett"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000002",
    "like_count": "4",
    "media_id": "17908471263905517",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Owen has not stopped talking about that sim. You may have started something. Don't tell Brett.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-13T19:32:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000004",
    "username": "hannah"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000003",
    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "17935062948170263",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Worth getting up for. Mom's right about the walk and you know it. Beautiful morning.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-15T08:11:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000004",
    "username": "hannah"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000004",
    "like_count": "5",
    "media_id": "17912648305571294",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Send your mother a copy for the hallway — she's been after a good course shot for weeks.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-13T20:51:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "judith"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000005",
    "like_count": "15",
    "media_id": "17923085164729038",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Lily by the koi pond is the best thing I've seen all week. Frame that one.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-11T17:32:03+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "kelsey"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000006",
    "like_count": "8",
    "media_id": "17914738205619480",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "The placards came out clean. You and the crew did right by that airplane, Dad.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-10T19:20:11+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "brett"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000007",
    "like_count": "3",
    "media_id": "17926093481750629",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "An 84 walking 18 at your age. Walt can keep the putt, you keep the round.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-06T18:09:44+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "kelsey"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000008",
    "like_count": "12",
    "media_id": "17904851972063418",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Sedona without me? We're settling this on the next trip. Glad you two got out.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-28T23:41:18+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "kelsey"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000009",
    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "17904851972063418",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000008",
    "text": "We'll bring you both next time. Your mother already picked the lunch spot.",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-01T00:15:52+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "judith"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000010",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "17919528046137852",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "He talked about that ramp tour for a week straight. Thank you for the patience, Dad.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-10T03:02:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "brett"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000011",
    "like_count": "4",
    "media_id": "17913947602581394",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Best weekend we've had in a while. Daniel's already asking when we come back.",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-18T04:28:33+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "kelsey"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000012",
    "like_count": "9",
    "media_id": "17922081463957204",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "The pie held up. The kitchen did not. Worth every minute of it.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T22:47:09+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "judith"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000013",
    "like_count": "5",
    "media_id": "17934759021648537",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "We missed the pie out here. Send leftovers. Or at least the recipe.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-27T23:18:41+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000004",
    "username": "hannah"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000014",
    "like_count": "11",
    "media_id": "17928604157392845",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Turn the volume up for that one. That radial sounds incredible when it catches.",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-29T20:51:36+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "brett"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000015",
    "like_count": "7",
    "media_id": "17903816492057613",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "He didn't sleep for two days after you left. Come back soon, Dad.",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-16T03:14:22+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000004",
    "username": "hannah"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000016",
    "like_count": "3",
    "media_id": "17931760284915037",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Those school groups are lucky to have you up there. You make it look easy.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-19T21:06:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "kelsey"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000017",
    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "17907364819250476",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "A morning of nothing is the whole point of retirement. You earned it.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-03T17:44:15+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "judith"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000018",
    "like_count": "4",
    "media_id": "17905719384260517",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Three balls in January? That's restraint for Tom. Good start to the year.",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-02T19:51:40+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "brett"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000019",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "17916283095471026",
    "parent_id": "",
    "text": "Tell Ed I said hello. Same stories, same two captains. Glad he made it out.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-15T01:22:09+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "kelsey"
  }
]